{"word":"G5411 - φόρος - phóros - for'-os - Tribute","slug":"G5411","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">φόρος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>phóros"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>for'-os"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Tribute"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C6;&#x03BF;&#x0301;&#x03C1;&#x03BF;&#x03C2; - phoros</b> - <i>for'-os</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G5342\">G5342</a>; a <i>load</i> (as <i>borne</i>), that is, (figuratively) a <i>tax</i> (properly an individual <i>assessment</i> on persons or property; whereas <a href=\"#/G5056\">G5056</a> is usually a general <i>toll</i> on goods or travel): - tribute."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1308\">G1308</a>, <a href=\"#/G1313\">G1313</a>, <a href=\"#/G2018\">G2018</a>, <a href=\"#/G399\">G399</a>, <a href=\"#/G4374\">G4374</a>, <a href=\"#/G4376\">G4376</a>, <a href=\"#/G4851\">G4851</a>, <a href=\"#/G5342\">G5342</a>, <a href=\"#/G5409\">G5409</a>, <a href=\"#/G5412\">G5412</a>, <a href=\"#/G5413\">G5413</a>, <a href=\"#/G5414\">G5414</a>"}]}